  "keyFeatures": [
    "Handler-based middleware (no complex traits or generics)",
    "Tree-based routing with per-branch middleware",
    "First-class OpenAPI support via #[endpoint] macro",
    "HTTP/1, HTTP/2, and HTTP/3 (QUIC) support",
    "Auto TLS via ACME (Let's Encrypt)",
    "WebSocket and WebTransport support",
    "JWT authentication middleware",
    "Built-in rate limiting, CORS, CSRF, sessions",
    "Async-first, built on Hyper and Tokio",
    "Zero unsafe code"
